                    <span>I am an experienced programmer with 10 experience.  However my knowledge was mainly desktop development (statistical application).  This book was an excellent introduction for me.  The examples are basic but clear.  I would happily buy another book by Scott Mitchell.  I now feel that I undertand all of the basic and I'm ready for something more advanced.  Reading the other reviews I cannot see how anyone can give this book only one star - it's positioned as an introductory book and it does this job well.</span>
                  
